INTRODUCTION
This assignment implements AERT toolkit using recursion and efficiency analysis.

STACK ADT
Stack is an Abstract Data Type. Operations push, pop, peek take O(1) time.

FACTORIAL
Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(n)

FIBONACCI
Naive Time: O(2^n)
Memoized Time: O(n)
Naive is slow because it recalculates same values.

TOWER OF HANOI
Moves = 2^n - 1
Time: O(2^n)
Space: O(n)

BINARY SEARCH
Time: O(log n)
Best: O(1)

PARADIGMS
Binary Search → Divide & Conquer
Fibonacci Memo → Dynamic Programming
Hanoi → Recursion

CONCLUSION
Recursion and memoization improve efficiency significantly.